     C                     Z-ADDA1TSQM    ABTSQM
     C                     Z-ADDA1TSQ#    ABTSQ#
     C                     Z-ADDA1SCYY    ABSCYY
     C                     Z-ADDA1SCMM    ABSCMM
     C                     Z-ADDA1SCDD    ABSCDD
     C                     Z-ADDA1SCTM    ABSCTM
      *
